    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of personality? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to hit the road! It has served its previous owners well and shows some honest signs of use, but it remains a solid choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a great value. Perfect for a first car or a practical commuter!",
